These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, d&b
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, may
There are 2 different favourite colors: emerald, azure
2 different pets are kept: horse, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
2. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in may is the fan of salsa##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Music-Genre      | salsa  | d&b   |
| Birthday   | may     | september   |
| Color         | azure | emerald |
| Pet     | horse | hedgehog    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
City: marseilles, london
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, fonseca
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up
House: townhouse, wooden
1. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
2. the vegafina-smoker is the wooden house##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| City          | marseilles     | london |
| Cigar   | fonseca | vegafina  |
| Beverage           | 7up         | soy-milk     |
| House     | townhouse   | wooden    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, fishing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, gospel
2 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble
City: prague, london
1. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Hobby    | fishing     | skydiving |
| Music-Genre         | gospel | pop    |
| Game         | backgammon         | scrabble        |
| City   | prague         | london    |

 #################################

 
