3. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Transport      | roller     | airplane |
| House          | futuristic   | ranch-style  |
| Pet         | goat | mouse     |
| Birthday   | november  | april         |

